                          <a href="/account/Drogen" id="action_accountMenu?account=Drogen&subject=RE%3A+How+to+get+better+chances+of+Success+without+Accelerators%3F%21&from=threadAccount9079378&threadId=1277258" class="action" onclick="return false">Drogen</a>
                        </td>
                        <td width="100%" class="farRightCell">
                          <span id="subjectNode_9079378" style="font-weight:bold;">RE: How to get better chances of Success without Accelerators?!</span><br>
                          Mar 9 2008, 10:55 AM EDT<br>
                          <span class="threadText" id="textNode_9079378">i forgot an other good advice for guys who want to upgrade more then one expensive items with this technique:<br>
                          <br>
                          When you loose an expensive item after you tried to upgrade it after 2 failures in row you simple got 3 failures in row! So DONT put a level 1 broadsword in for the next upgrade!!!!!!!!!!!!! it will be a waste for this good chance. Just put the next expensive item in that you want to upgrade. If this will fail (ugh... really bad luck) put the next expensive in the sucess rate will be know nearly 100%<br>
                          <br>
                          You should consider this too when you want to test this technique with the 20x Level 1 Broadsword and the 10x Level 2 Broadswords.</span> <span class="controlsNode" id="controlsNode_9079378" rel="false"><span class="controlsNode"></span></span>
